nodes.text: Club Deeja was an entertainment establishment in the city of Keren on the planet Naboo. During the Galactic Civil War, the club was owned by Mul Sanaka and protected by a number of Besalisk guards, including Snes. Melodic Order, a cloister of Alderaanians, performed via hologram at the club. Princess Leia Organa traveled to Club Deeja after the destruction of Alderaan in order to rescue the Alderaanians there from the Galactic Empire.
